# Redirect domain aliases to primary domain
https://www.lpmori.com/* https://www.leonardopaccianimori.com/:splat 301!
https://lpmori.com/* https://www.leonardopaccianimori.com/:splat 301!

# These extra rules are required because HTTPS is not forced
http://www.lpmori.com/* https://www.leonardopaccianimori.com/:splat 301!
http://lpmori.com/* https://www.leonardopaccianimori.com/:splat 301!

